# Book Store Application

This app is a simulation of a bookstore where users can view the available books, check out books, and the check in books.

## Features of this program..

- This program shows the available books.
- Shows checked out books.
- Allows users to check out a book by entering in their name.
- Check in a book which allows users to check in a book that they have previously checked out.
- Lastly, it allows the users to exit the application.

- Welcome to Book Store.
  1. Press 1 to Show Available Books.
  2. Press 2 to Show Checked out Books.
  3. Press 3 to Exit.
  Select an option:


